{
  "stem": "21008.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when she started there, or when she-- when she went for the interview there, she told the boss right away who she was and who her husband is and who her child is right away.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the man said, that doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You can work for us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was very good to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't-- I wouldn't call him a Nazi, no.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But he was a German man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was nice and helpful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a German man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He has-- yes, he-- he had a business.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Actually, it was a very famous stationery in the old city of Berlin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The name was very famous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes, now we could pay rent, and we could pay for the food that we got on-- on ration-- ration cards which was very little.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's another thing to talk about.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But at least we had some money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were talking '39?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Well, of course, even earlier you couldn't go to the theaters.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't go to the movies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You couldn't go to parks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All the park benches had signs on 'Not for Jews.' Couldn't sit in a park.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Many, many restaurants had signs, 'Jews and dogs are not desired,' you know, or undesirable or whatever, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You couldn't go [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] anywhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, Berlin has a beautiful surroundings with a lot of water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There are always boats.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You wouldn't go on boats.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I learned to ice skate in the winter of 1934.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother wanted me to learn how to swim in the summer of '35.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she took me to the local pool or swimming school or whatever, and the first question was 'Is that child Jewish?' And my mother said, yes.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And well, we won't teach Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
